15
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:39,673
R-Really?

16
00:00:39,675 --> 00:00:41,540
Get out of my store.

17
00:00:41,542 --> 00:00:42,817
Now.

18
00:00:45,387 --> 00:00:47,754
ADULT SHELDON: <i>In every young man's life,</i>

19
00:00:47,757 --> 00:00:51,000
