00:11:37,638 --> 00:11:38,933
about how we get around her.

277
00:11:38,935 --> 00:11:40,100
Which won't be easy,

278
00:11:40,102 --> 00:11:43,070
because she's got Jesus on her team.

279
00:11:43,072 --> 00:11:45,308
Boy howdy.

